    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "1000mg of acetaminophen? that seems like a lot for one time but okay. i'll try the magnesium too. do u think i should take anything else to help with the neck stiffness? maybe some aspirin or something? i just want to be able to sleep this off and stop feeling so weird.",
